I refuse to reveal much of the plot, as this is the best if viewed yourself. Expect a plurality of plot pivots, supremely spellbinding sub plots and dishes of disinformation. I would definitely recommend this anime to everyone on Earth. It surpasses genre, and even anime itself. I feel that it fails to describe the artistic value of this anime.
